{"id":591081,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【立此存照】稳住学生，维护学院荣誉/","date":"2018-07-30T19:24:43Z","modified":"2018-07-30T19:54:05Z","title":"【立此存照】稳住学生，维护学院荣誉","content":"<div class=\"WB_info\"><a class=\"W_f14 W_fb S_txt1\" href=\"https://weibo.com/fangkc?refer_flag=1005055014_\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@方可成</a> <i class=\"W_icon icon_approve\" title=\"微博个人认证 \"></i> 7月29日 14:13 来自 微博 weibo.com</div>\n<div class=\"WB_text W_f14\">\n<p>广外陈国昌被指性骚扰之后，学校的应对方式是：稳住学生，禁止学生干部转发相关内容，要将对事件处理的主动权牢牢掌握在自己手里，尽力减少舆论的关注。</p>\n<p>说辞是“维护学院荣誉”、“避免造成恐慌”。</p>\n<p>声明中的最后一段还不忘厉声警告举报者。</p>\n<p>如果这就是是“大鸣大放大字报”，真没见过这么憋屈的“大鸣大放大字报”。</p>\n<p>既然他们要消声，要恐吓，那我们就加油多传播吧。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-591085\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Capture-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Capture-1.png 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Capture-1-300x177.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Capture-1-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-591084\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u2ic4j20cw0m8wfq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"862\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u2ic4j20cw0m8wfq.jpg 464w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u2ic4j20cw0m8wfq-174x300.jpg 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-591082\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u7umnj20ku0p6tbn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u7umnj20ku0p6tbn.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/61f13edfly1ftqp7u7umnj20ku0p6tbn-248x300.jpg 248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 